snippet.title: BattleSky Brigade: Tribes -  Campaign System
snippet.description:
This is the other project we've been working on (and that's still in progress!). 

It's a multiplayer strategy game where you defend your shared guild resources against other guilds in order to build the strongest BattleSky Brigade.

Quick update video about various features thus far.
